1
00:01:40,947 --> 00:01:42,710
Dismissed.

2
00:01:44,818 --> 00:01:46,115
Boys.

3
00:01:46,686 --> 00:01:50,622
Remember this, when Mr. Butterbass
calls you to attention...

4
00:01:50,791 --> 00:01:54,659
...I want to see every eyelid snap.
- Yes, sir.

5
00:01:54,995 --> 00:01:56,826
Take your posts.

6
00:02:01,501 --> 00:02:05,961
- Good morning, young ladies.
- Good morning, Mr. Hammerstein.

7
00:02:12,813 --> 00:02:15,008
About face.

8
00:02:29,463 --> 00:02:33,763
That is one thing
I will not tolerate in this hotel.

9
00:02:37,704 --> 00:02:39,331
Dismissed.

10
00:02:42,476 --> 00:02:45,445
And now, the band.

11
00:02:45,612 --> 00:02:48,046
Right over here.

12
00:03:02,229 --> 00:03:03,856
Good morning, Popeye.

13
00:03:04,030 --> 00:03:07,659
How dare you speak
when I have not asked you a question.

14
00:03:07,834 --> 00:03:11,065
Now then, I have had several complaints
about all of you.

15
00:03:12,038 --> 00:03:14,131
That's funny.
No one has complained me.

16
00:03:14,307 --> 00:03:15,331
Silence.

17
00:03:15,509 --> 00:03:17,875
I will dismiss, discharge and disqualify...

18
00:03:18,044 --> 00:03:21,013
...any employee
who gets familiar with the guests.

19
00:03:21,181 --> 00:03:23,911
But what happens
if the guests get familiar with us?

20
00:03:24,251 --> 00:03:26,981
- Quiet.
- Please.

21
00:03:27,554 --> 00:03:31,046
I have been imported from Switzerland
by the management of this hotel...

22
00:03:31,224 --> 00:03:33,124
...to enforce discipline...

23
00:03:33,293 --> 00:03:35,488
...and I will.

24
00:03:36,229 --> 00:03:37,958
Where is the boss of this outfit?

25
00:03:38,131 --> 00:03:43,694
Where is that loafer, Roger Bond,
and his assistant loafer, Fred Ayres?

26
00:03:43,870 --> 00:03:46,338
Coming right down.

27
00:04:01,588 --> 00:04:03,522
Yeah.

28
00:04:04,958 --> 00:04:07,984
- How do you feel, boy?
- Yeah.

29
00:04:08,161 --> 00:04:10,425
Well, this is all in one piece.

30
00:04:10,597 --> 00:04:13,896
That's more than we'll be if we don't
get to that hotel in 29 seconds.

31
00:04:14,067 --> 00:04:15,796
Come on, kid, will you?

32
00:04:19,739 --> 00:04:23,038
Well, why don't he put
a kitchenette and bath in here?

33
00:04:23,209 --> 00:04:26,804
- Crazy, I guess.
- Crazy nothing. That guy writes songs.

34
00:04:26,980 --> 00:04:28,675
Well, that's screwy, ain't it?

35
00:04:28,848 --> 00:04:33,547
It's so screwy
that he can buy a plane just like this.

36
00:04:34,487 --> 00:04:35,715
No touch.

37
00:04:54,074 --> 00:04:57,339
In just 10 seconds they go on the air.

38
00:04:57,544 --> 00:05:01,310
If those two loafers aren't here
I'm going to fire them.

39
00:05:01,481 --> 00:05:03,847
One, to make ready...

40
00:05:04,017 --> 00:05:05,917
...two, to go...

41
00:05:10,957 --> 00:05:13,824
Five, six, pick up sticks.

42
00:05:19,699 --> 00:05:21,189
Afternoon, ladies and gentlemen.

43
00:05:21,368 --> 00:05:25,930
This is Roger Bond and his Yankee Clippers
from the Date Grove of the Hotel Hibiscus...

44
00:05:26,106 --> 00:05:27,971
...at Miami, Florida.

45
00:05:28,141 --> 00:05:30,735
We offer for your pleasure
as our first selection...

46
00:05:30,910 --> 00:05:33,777
..."Music Makes Me,"
with a complete vocalization...

47
00:05:33,947 --> 00:05:36,609
...by that charming, bubbling,
effervescent little lady...

48
00:05:36,783 --> 00:05:40,913
...Miss Honey Hale. Contact.

49
00:05:50,930 --> 00:05:55,799
<i>In me you see a sinner</i>
<i>And dancing is my crime</i>

50
00:05:55,969 --> 00:06:00,736
<i>It seems a sin I've got to give in</i>
<i>To syncopated time</i>

51
00:06:00,907 --> 00:06:05,674
<i>It makes me lose my dignity</i>
<i>It makes me lose my poise</i>

52
00:06:05,845 --> 00:06:10,680
<i>Some folks call it music</i>
<i>My folks call it noise</i>

53
00:06:11,017 --> 00:06:14,680
<i>I like music, old and new</i>

54
00:06:14,854 --> 00:06:19,120
<i>But music makes me do the things</i>
<i>I never should do</i>

55
00:06:19,292 --> 00:06:23,854
<i>Oh, I like music, sweet and blue</i>

56
00:06:24,030 --> 00:06:28,933
<i>But music makes me do the things</i>
<i>I never should do</i>

57
00:06:29,235 --> 00:06:31,999
<i>My self-control</i>
<i>was something to brag about</i>

58
00:06:32,172 --> 00:06:33,969
<i>Now it's a gag about town</i>

59
00:06:34,140 --> 00:06:39,510
<i>The things I do are never forgiven</i>
<i>And just when I'm living them down</i>

60
00:06:39,746 --> 00:06:43,147
<i>I hear music, then I'm through</i>

61
